  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You focus your chakra through your visual senses, protecting yourself and any allies within 10 feet of you from blindness and visual illusions. For the duration, affected creatures are immune to the blinded condition and have advantage on saving throws against genjutsu with the Visual keyword. You do not need to spend chakra to concentrate on this jutsu if your Junsugan is active.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D- Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the radius by 5 feet. If you cast this jutsu at B-Rank, it instead lasts for up to 1 hour. If you cast this jutsu at S-Rank, it no longer requires concentration to maintain.</p>",
